nus.sins2.device.ftr201

Class FilterStageDeviceParameters

  • java.lang.Object
    • nus.sins2.device.ftr201.FilterStageDeviceParameters

  • public final class FilterStageDeviceParameters
extends java.lang.Object
    NUS SINS.2 FilterStage Device parameter data.

    For local data storage of device parameter data.

    The locator is the IPV4 address of the Moxa Modbus/TCP gateway. The axisno is the axis number (0..15) for the IAI controller on the Modbus/RTU bus.
